            <h3 class="modern-card-title">Airport</h3>
            <p class="modern-card-description"> The company’s ₹3500 Crore estimate for the airport market is a credible target for its comprehensive E&M solutions, extending beyond just AGL. With the global commercial airport lighting market valued at USD 700–750 million in 2024 (~₹5800–₹6200 Crores) and India projected to grow at over 9.4% CAGR (IMARC, Jan 2024), this estimate aligns well within a growing aviation infrastructure sector.</p>
            <a href="/airport" class="modern-card-button">View Details</a>
